{"tid":911332,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"日日通宵自然醒vs成日OT訓到唔知醒？","createTime":"2018-11-22T00:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T14:08:25.000Z","uid":43412,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"df9bdf31d62a7622c03370385a462fd7c81ee565","tid":911332,"uid":43412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:19:25.000Z","msg":"我今日同個耐冇見嘅朋友傾計，聽到佢返通宵，就即刻覺得佢辛苦又傷身，但傾傾下，我又覺得好似唔係咁。<br />\n<br />\n先唔論人工、多唔多野做嘅程度，純粹講健康，究竟通宵但訓夠傷身啲，定係訓得五六個鐘正常天黑訓覺傷身啲？<br />\n<br />\nBtw我見佢又唔覺得佢好殘，或者可能係後山未睇得出住？<br />\n<br />\n有冇醫生解答下"},{"pid":"4d635d609fb2f12d5aefe13d8c6be65d550b1ed7","tid":911332,"uid":80535,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:28:17.000Z","msg":"咪一撚樣"},{"pid":"dc28c64a43cbfaae191190666467890a63706479","tid":911332,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:31:21.000Z","msg":"我都想知返通宵夠瞓<br />\n應該好過朝早唔夠瞓 行屍走肉咁去返工"},{"pid":"50399822acb404b551f963ce00f71cbeaa8cbea0","tid":911332,"uid":25641,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:34:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6cd79f3f33ac2d6c146aec737132558c607d589","tid":911332,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:34:43.000Z","msg":"其實夠瞓好過唔夠瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c90f69eb6ea4d5ebe1e2415fd47c874a8e60a0","tid":911332,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:36:43.000Z","msg":"緊係唔夠訓傷身啲<br />\n你日頭係間黑房訓其實同夜晚訓一樣有效"},{"pid":"a1e00a7500d5e1d6081d115776134be05cbbee58","tid":911332,"uid":43412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc28c64a43cbfaae191190666467890a63706479","tid":911332,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:31:21.000Z","msg":"我都想知返通宵夠瞓<br />\n應該好過朝早唔夠瞓 行屍走肉咁去返工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:54:35.000Z","msg":"我都有啲咁講得 冇咩精神返工 好辛苦下"},{"pid":"653995f331d5956a62ecd364559d5e9a575a9890","tid":911332